Action Example : { type: RATE_COURSE, rating: simple_or_complex_object }

Action Creator:

    rateCourse(rating) {
      return { type: RATE_COURSE, rating: rating };
    }

    Action creator name and action name should be same (convention)


Creating Redux Store:
  let store = createStore(reducer);    // Placed in application's entry point.


Redux Store:
  store.dispatch(action)
  store.subscribe(listener)
  store.getState()
  replaceReducer(nextReducer)
